column5: Does anyone happen to know if the Walmart in Dryden is open 24 hours a day? For this year's Savant Lake trip, we're going to save money by leaving the night of 7/6 and driving all the way to West Caribou Air without staying overnight somewhere. We usually stock up on snacks and stuff at the Dryden WallyWorld, but we'll be going through there in the wee hours of the morning and I want to make sure it's going to be open!
The Walmart in Dryden is open till 9 or 10 pm,not 24 hrs,sorry
Thanks - that's what I needed to know! We'll just have to get our stuff in Bemidji before we leave. It'll be cheaper that way anyway
Wal-Mart, Store InformationStreet: Highway 17 EastDryden, on P8N1A1-Phone: (807) 223-7190
http://www.walmart.ca/homeLink to the store hours.\...search for the Dryden store.
